Package: txtools
Title: An interface between GenomicAlignments and transcriptomic representations
Version: 0.0.8.1
Date: 2020-22-12
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miguel Angel",
           family = "Garcia-Campos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "angel.campos@ciencias.unam.mx",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5223-8174", 
                       webpage = "https://angelcampos.github.io/"))
Description: txtools extends the functionality of GenomicAlignments and 
    GenomicAlignments by filtering and processing RNA-seq reads aligned to a 
    genome into their transcriptomic counterparts and allows generating 
    easy-handling summarized tables.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
